Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">小姐姐靓丽的穿搭，休闲时尚，长相精致甜美可人</p><p><img src=\"http://p8.qhimg.com/t01b521170d6639584c.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">小姐姐身姿曼妙，穿粉色紧身连衣裙，性感又迷人</p><p><img src=\"http://p9.qhimg.com/t01a2c2bc89af3cc571.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这一位白皙脸蛋的小姐姐，搭配前卫潮流。头上架着黑色墨镜，身穿针织长袖搭配一条吊带裙，脚上穿着一双黑色短靴，走在路上充满了自信</p><p><img src=\"http://p0.qhimg.com/t014d1c641e07356da4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图片来源于网络</p><p><br/></p>', '1565946367');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('216', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果这世界上有一种服装无论昂贵与否，都可以让广大女性为之疯狂的话，那它就应该是婚纱了吧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950666259199.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为了留下曾经相爱的时光很多的新人情侣们都喜欢在结婚纪念日的时候在拍摄几张婚纱照，为了在老去的时候能跟着爱人坐在一起看着曾经的美好，而不是记忆就这么的匆匆而去什么都没有留下来。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950666441155.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以，婚纱对很多女性来说不只是一件衣服，更像是一种承诺，一种对爱的承诺。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950667876376.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190816/1565950667427580.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这世界上贵重的东西有很多，但是曾经的回忆却是无价的。而如果能在结婚的时候拍一组美丽的婚纱照，估计很多人也就没有遗憾了。大家都喜欢怎样的婚纱呢？欢迎在评论区留言讨论哦！</p><p><br/></p>', '1565950667');
