INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('395', '<p>头摄影是一种源于欧美国家的文化，最早是源于时尚杂志的需求，用相机捕捉街上的时尚元素，还要传递来自民间的流行信息，于是所谓“街头秀”就应运而生。一般来说，一次专业的街拍，必须捕捉到被拍者衣服的细节.搭配和牌子。如今街拍正成为国内年轻人一项新的街头文化.下面由老李街拍给大家奉献这期的精彩内容吧</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190903/1567491244225380.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>外国的小姐姐普通都是大高个子，也不知道为什么？今天的这一位，她穿得是一件白色的小吊带。上面没有一丁点的小花纹，在裤子上她穿的是一件短裤，看上去这条短裤并没有缝边。像是自己手工剪开的一样，脚上穿着一件粉色的高跟鞋。不是那种细高跟，这样的话踩着也是特别的稳当。</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190903/1567491245162903.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>时尚搭配的穿出女神呼之欲出的美，在街头你就是众人心中的女神，非常衬托女性的优雅甜美气质，时尚带给你靓丽的穿着体验，轻松帮你打造出窈窕的淑女风范，穿在身上是一种享受。/</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190903/1567491246912793.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>甜美时尚的紧身打底裤具有减龄的效果，魅力十足的一款，也彰显你的大气时尚的味道，而且腰部松紧腰设计能够满足更多女性的不同穿搭需求，随意搭配的打底裤美女穿出与平时不一样的格调。</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190903/1567491247732180.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>更多精彩内容敬请期待，喜欢的朋友请加个关注，转发是一种支持，点赞是一种鼓励，留个言你的帮助是我最大的动力，谢谢。</p><p><br/></p>', '1567491263');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('396', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高个子的女生出门逛街如何穿搭？南方稍微凉快一点的天气，街头时尚女生的装扮也有所收敛，夏日里的一些性感小衣服关进了小黑屋，但秋天也有好看养眼的穿搭方法，趁天气还不冷的情况下，再来吸引一波目光杀吧！</p><p><img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t013c99613698fb1897.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有人说个高的女人穿什么衣服都好看，可以凭借着自身的优势还衬托出衣服的美，对于这个观点，小编认为一半对一半错，个子高的女人也有很多种，比如：胖的、瘦的、长的、短的，穿搭仍然需要小技巧，不是照着别人依葫芦画瓢，走出来就是时尚，以下几位街头姐姐的出行穿搭就非常的完美，虽然有一点瑕疵，但看得出在一些小细节的地方花了小心思！</p><p><img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t0131d32e764c464c03.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">条纹束腰半身连衣裙 透明塑胶拖鞋</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这里的透明塑胶拖鞋，并不是90年代的那种塑胶鞋！图中的姐姐身材修长，如果半身连衣裙选择太鲜艳的话，可爱清纯的小清流就会荡然无存。这一身的搭配氛围刚刚好，透明的拖鞋不仅时尚而且舒适，加上束腰型的半身连衣裙，无论是俏皮可爱，还是性感小心机，都能够轻松地控制住小气场！</p><p><img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01cca16b5754e12792.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">白色紧身包臀裙 灰白色绑带中跟鞋</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">敢穿包臀裙上街的姐姐，显然对自己的身材很有自信心，走在马路上不害羞，直接无视别人的异样目光，最害怕的是吸引不了路人的一点关注。白色紧身的包臀裙对于高个子的女生来说，本身就是对外者的一种诱惑，灰白色的中跟鞋有那么一点点的不完美，如果能换上一双红色的露趾鞋，或者白色的露趾鞋，相信走在大马路的引流的量会更多一些！</p><p><img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t017fe8f1e548770459.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">透明花边连衣裙 粉色低帮鞋</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一眼望去最惹人注目的就是上半身的透明连衣裙，袖口的花边可爱设计，再加上下摆的透明花边，关注者的第一印象就是“云山不知深处”，其中最出色在于V领的设计，图中的姐姐身材没得说，但如果换成身材丰满的成熟女性来穿的话，相信韵味会更升一级。透明花边连衣裙搭配上粉色低帮鞋，虽然舒适度有了，美中不足是地失去了一丝成熟韵味感！</p><p><img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01c3c0c73aa3967598.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">米色丝织连衣裙 米色的平底尖鞋</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">走在时尚的街头，不顾世人的世俗目光，只顾低头看着自己的手机，如此放荡不羁的态度，早已展示出了自己的独特个性，虽然米黄色的衣服不能展示太多的时尚元素，但素雅的一身，给路人的是一种舒适感，在米色连衣裙与米色平底鞋的搭配下，瞬间秒变成时尚清纯的可人儿，不要问我为什么，因为米色是我表哥！</p><p><img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01bdc7899745c1e814.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">白色T恤 白色露趾休闲鞋</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对一个有小心机的女人来说，只要有展现自己美的机会就一定不能错过，图中的姐姐，小心机十足，丰满的上半身加上紧身露肚脐的白色T恤，到底是想宣誓自己的单纯，还是完美的身材，幸好白色露趾休闲鞋收敛了一点性感，否则在你身边的女人，看你的眼神一定会是愤怒！</p><p><img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t013a6e44187e1fb500.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高个子的女生，出行穿搭要根据自己的优势，把自己的优势无限放大，并不是每一次的穿搭都要达到一百分，很时候不需要百分百的完美，会留一点瑕疵的女人才是真正的高手，因为时尚界本就没有完美！</p><p><br/></p>', '1567585915');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('397', '<p>翻了这么久真没觉得有几个好看的，发现大家追求的都是细长腿，有的实在太瘦了，像骷髅一样，让我这种可能由于自身骨架大所以观感变化的人感觉腿太细了，太脆弱了，撑起上面的部分好累的。一昧追求细长，小腿正面看完全就是你骨头的描边，腰臀线条啥也没有，p得死白死白，两根麻杆儿似的。。。<br/></p><p>私以为女孩子本就该下半身比上半身壮，这样也才更好看，在肤色上我也总是容易喜欢那种被阳光晒过的颜色（笑哭</p><p>来个米宝的腿吧，这真的是我个人觉得最好看最最喜欢的类型：不一定要有多长，比例合适就够了，腿上要有肉感，匀称较直且给人感觉有力量，有好看的肌肉线条，漂亮的膝盖，屁股收紧，不要有病态或者松垮的感觉。</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589795515328.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"850\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589795224740.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"850\"/></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589795114145.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1000\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589796498515.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1000\"/></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589796680218.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589796946987.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\"/></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589796196785.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589796624940.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\"/></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589796699507.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190904/1567589796121836.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '1567589815');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('398', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不知从何时开始，“隐居”成为一种潮流。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">日日穿梭在都市的车水马龙中，为富贵权名折腰，实在太<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">俗</span>。倒不如脱去一身西装，换上粗布麻衣，古风长袍，回归自然田园，与清风明月相伴，悠然自得，岂不惬意。</p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-6e2ea4022cb7bcc3?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/1080/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-e398aaca62665e8c?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/1080/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“红尘俗世今看透。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“此间一别，终南山见。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“品诗酒花茶，赏风雪雨蛙。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“远离俗世的浮躁与喧嚣，收获内心的纯真和安静。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.......</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">朋友圈晒着如画的风景照片，和闲适的田园生活，再搭配诗一样的文字，总能惹来一大堆点赞和艳羡的目光：大冰说得没错，这世界上真的有人过着我想要的生活。</p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-263c575e35914390?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">必须承认，不管是隐居还是回归田园，都不是一件坏事，追求岁月静好也是人生的一种选择，只是大多数人的离开，却是建立在“隐居可解百忧”的思想上。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">创业失败，恋情受挫，工作压力大，心情烦躁.....所有的糟心事，好像逃进深山田野，便可烟消云散，原地顿悟。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">是不管不顾的一时兴起，是未曾经历过的突发奇想。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">/01/</h4><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">隐居之前，我们先来谈谈钱。</span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此前朋友就告诉我，认识的人因为存款不足，从终南山回家了，当时还不以为意。近日却又看到新闻，说一位隐居终南山的姑娘，因为租借的小院年租金从400涨到2万，没什么经济来源的她，不得不放弃隐居计划，重新回到城市找工作。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-9a5d4e4b2173389e?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p>姑娘住的房子，图片来源：@九点半</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着隐居人士的增多，终南山的房租也跟着水涨船高，一年的租金对于很多辞职没有收入的人来说，就是一道迈不过的门坎。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">讲真，我知道的所有逃离北上广，或者隐居终南山可以过得很好的人，除了自己内心坚定想要这种生活以外，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">都有养活自己的一技之长：</span>或者绘画，或者摄影，或者设计，或者已经是小有名气的自媒体人......</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">没钱不可以隐居吗？可以，只是对大多数人并不适用。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一年四季，没有空调暖气，每天的伙食都是地里种的青菜土豆西红柿（前提是你得会种菜），想吃顿肉还要想一下自己的存款余额.....</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然，对很多人来说生活条件差一点不是什么事，但<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">如果你生病了呢？如果你的父母生病了呢？如果你和伴侣有孩子了呢.........</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-d2254e7ed24a3f2d?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">网上有个很火的帖子：<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">你从什么时候开始，觉得钱很重要？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">想给妈妈买个她喜欢的手镯，但钱包里空空如也时；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因为没钱去医院,一个人发烧躺在床上硬抗时；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看到喜欢的东西却又买不起时</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">想给她一个未来时</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.......</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">没有好好思量好，便不管不顾的投入到隐居大军中去，想要采菊东篱下，悠然见南山，但大多数时候却只能晨兴理荒秽，带月荷锄归，最终结果还是草盛豆苗稀。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在经济能力不足以让你可以肆无忌惮挥霍自己的冲动时，你需要解决的永远是眼前的苟且。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">/02/</span></h4><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">逃离隐居，不是包治百病的“神药”。</span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">“麦家理想谷”里讲过一个真实的故事：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一位逃离北上广的姑娘，辞职后在大理买下了一个农场，每天种草、养花、骑马.....自由自在无拘无束，惹来一片羡慕的声音，觉得那才是生活。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然而过了不久，有人去看她时，却发现农场一片荒芜，到处是马屎，马更是饿得瘦骨嶙峋....那场景，完全颠覆了人们的想象。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">姑娘表示每天除草，给马清理屎尿实在太烦太累了，不想干了......</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">逃离与远方，听上去总是充满美好，现在生活中的所有问题，似乎都可以瞬间解决。然而事实上是，大多数人的逃离，不过是把远方变成新一轮的苟且。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-087ab77c00776de9?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">今年4月份，一位三十多岁的小哥在山上的一个废弃小屋里被警察发现，他原是重庆大学的学生，因为沉迷小说导致学业荒废被退学。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">退学后，小哥跟着亲戚外出打工，但打工也并不顺利，觉得生活没意思的他索性躲进了深山，开始了与世隔绝的隐士生活——饿了吃干面包，渴了喝山泉水，没事干就看小说，累了就睡觉.......</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">张嘉佳《老情书》里有一段情节始终印象深刻，酒吧里一位老太太拄着拐棍，痛骂年轻人：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">我就特别看不起你们这帮年轻人，二三十岁就叨叨说平平淡淡才是真。你们配吗？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">老和尚说终归要见山是山，但你们经历见山不是山了吗？不趁着年轻拔腿就在，去刀山火海，不入世就自以为出世，以为自己是活佛涅槃来的？我的平平淡淡是苦出来的，你们的平平淡淡是懒惰，是害怕，是贪图安逸，是一条不敢见世面的土狗。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">就算是陶渊明，也先后出仕共计五次，经历了官场的沉沉浮浮，最终窥见内心真正的追求，寻得真正的平静。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-c9ecd2e9876a73dd?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">西安长安区政协委员，长安道教协会秘书长梁兴扬在微博里写道：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这几天不少朋友问我终南山做隐士的途径，这样说吧，做隐士首先你要是一个“士”，功成名遂身退可也；连自己的人生都没理清楚，连做人都没学会，人样都没活出来，偏激迷信逃避懦弱，还要隐。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">远方很美好，累了的话可以暂且放下问题，让自己休息一段时间，但不要将它作为解决问题的唯一方法，作为接下来生活的全部。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">真正的成熟永远是，学会对自己的生活负责，学会心平气和的面对兵荒马乱，而不是逃避。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">/03/</span></h4><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; font-size: 20px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">大隐隐于市，小隐隐于野。</span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有人总觉得自由和平静，是一件很遥远的事情，所以得去山上，得去远方，得逃离北上广，只有到了淳朴的地方浮躁的内心才能得到安宁。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但真正的宁静自由，不在山上，不在远方，而是在每天的柴米油盐，实实在在生活中。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">很久以前看到过一个姑娘，一个人在外面打拼，因为没什么钱，租了一个小房子。工作并不轻松，也时常与那个繁华喧嚣的都市格格不入，但这都不妨碍她把生活过得有滋有味。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在钢筋水泥坚硬的城市里，为自己打造了一个温暖的世外桃源。</p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-8f5cd788898f2418?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">那些废弃的铁罐，摇身一变，立刻生机盎然。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-482f0d18cd5025ce?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">零散的木块用胶水组合，亦可以成为独一无二的相框，成为了生活里不期而遇的小惊喜。</p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-3b06372491814703?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">买不起几万块钱的餐桌没关系，为自己认真准备一顿美食，插一朵花，一样能在最普通寻常的日子里活出甜味、活出雅致、活出清欢。</p><p><img class=\"\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/18529258-6cfe5f04ec8a7028?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《BEAMS AT HOME》开头描述了一段温暖而美好的生活场景：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在家里做的事：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">清晨醒来，烧开水冲入现磨的咖啡豆；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">咬着吐司，给蕨类植物和仙人球随便浇点水；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">到中午，晾晒的衣服刷拉拉地随风飘动，猫咪寻着阳光充足的地方团成一团。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">傍晚到家，从屋外看到屋内的灯光，孩子们跑到玄关前迎接；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">和家人互相问候着“我回来啦。”“你回来啦。”“今天吃生菜猪肉炖锅吧。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">之后边想着周末去哪儿，边收拾滑板和野营工具。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">深夜，泡个热水澡，香甜入眠……</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">浸透了人生每一天的那个场所，发生着各种故事。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这难道不是另一种修行，不盲目追名逐利，自有自己的生活节奏，好好地快乐度日，并从中发现生活的诗意。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">很多人说自己看破红尘，你红尘都未看完，又何来看破。</p><p><br/></p>', '1567662908');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('399', '<article>\n    <p class=\"info\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: gray; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01e92c36f72f324a01.jpg\" alt=\"t01e92c36f72f324a01.jpg?size=500x793\"/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        如果裙子是每个女生的最爱，那么旗袍就是裙子当中的白月光了，虽然说旗袍也是属于裙子的一种，但是旗袍对于女生的气质和身材就有很大的考验了，因为不仅是我们要根据自己的身材，挑选合适自己的旗袍，而且还要穿出了旗袍的美感，现在随着时间的发展，旗袍的款式也是越来越多了，各种款式的旗袍开始融入到我们的生活当中，而且还当作的日常单品穿搭。\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01d1b4f8ff395c73cb.jpg\" alt=\"t01d1b4f8ff395c73cb.jpg?size=500x805\"/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t0104542678217bc723.jpg\" alt=\"t0104542678217bc723.jpg?size=500x767\"/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01005201137a112de4.jpg\" alt=\"t01005201137a112de4.jpg?size=500x761\"/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01e0dc733f080b2247.jpg\" alt=\"t01e0dc733f080b2247.jpg?size=500x766\"/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t010b5e201c69d1f92c.jpg\" alt=\"t010b5e201c69d1f92c.jpg?size=500x783\"/>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <br/>\n    </p>\n</article>\n<p>\n    <span class=\"rbtn\">举报</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n    <br/>\n</p>', '1568615298');
