INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('520', '<p class=\"info\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: gray; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <br/>\n</p>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568714091827830.jpg\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    年轻活力的时尚辣妈，一件柠檬黄连衣裙，尽显时尚魅力。柠檬黄是今年夏天大火的一个颜色，黄色的干净，是现代许多女孩追求的一种时尚感。亮色在这两年都很受捧，尤其是这样像柠檬的颜色，给人一种夏日清新清凉的感觉。\n</p>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568714091785499.jpg\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    这位辣妈一件柠檬黄吊带连衣裙走在街上，一股夏日清新感扑面而来，亮色在夏天可以说是非常出彩的，不过柠檬黄的颜色很难驾驭，幸好辣妈皮肤白暂，柠檬黄更是显得辣妈气质倍增。在炎热的夏天里，不仅清凉气爽，走在街上，也十分吸睛。\n</p>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568714092919281.jpg\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    并且独特的领口和包臀设计，显得辣妈身材更加高挑。吊带的独特设计，露出辣妈优美的颈部线条，散发出浓浓的女人味。亮眼的穿搭风格，走在街上不仅会有着很高的回头率，也能散发出东方女人独有的韵味！\n</p>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568714092545257.jpg\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    辣妈侧身站在街头，随意的拨弄秀发，包包和高跟鞋同样选择亮色，银色的装饰更是显得整体造型清新有活力。墨镜更是给辣妈增添了一股高贵神秘感，走在街头，也能看出自信十足。\n</p>\n<p>\n    <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568714093868655.jpg\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    现在初秋时节，天气转凉，小编建议大家这样的穿搭出门搭配一件毛衣外套，不仅保暖，也不失时尚感。荧幕前的你学会了吗？\n</p>\n<p>\n    <br/>\n</p>', '1568714097');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('521', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    美丽的女生，天生丽质的她们，实际上在有的时候，用最简约的服装，勾勒己的轮廓，虽然十分简约，但却人了人们的想象空间，让路人不管从何角度看到她，都能感受到她一样的美感。\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01ed25d040177c2a74.jpg\" alt=\"t01ed25d040177c2a74.jpg?size=562x780\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t017231e13bb3932eca.jpg\" alt=\"t017231e13bb3932eca.jpg?size=561x790\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    美丽的她，一头秀发随着地垂在肩上，微风一吹，让她拥有了飘逸感，身材匀称的她，由一条简洁的包臀裙，让自己拥有了紧凑感，让她拥有了女神的自我风范。\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    她并不是一位丰腴型的女神，哪怕身着着与自己身材紧紧贴合的包展裙，仍然无法展现出足够的立体感。但黑色的裙子，还是在很大程度上提升了她的品质感，让她也拥有着十足的女人味。\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01b83c7982b0b770b8.jpg\" alt=\"t01b83c7982b0b770b8.jpg?size=565x790\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t018a98dca165f36122.jpg\" alt=\"t018a98dca165f36122.jpg?size=564x783\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    紧身款式的吊带包臀裙，让身材匀称的她，把她身材的轮廓美呈现在人们面前，让她的把女神完美的腰身、曼妙的形象，轻松刻在路人们的心里。\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    这样美丽的女神，打扮简约而时髦，脸上带着自信的笑容，显得十分有亲和力，与其他女生相比，她明显更加独特，白皙的肤色，曼妙的腰身，在包臀裙的加持之下，让她拥有了女神独特的韵味。\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01c9c5a5aabe25a8ba.jpg\" alt=\"t01c9c5a5aabe25a8ba.jpg?size=561x781\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <img src=\"https://p0.ssl.qhimgs4.com/t01f9703b8b54b5eb05.jpg\" alt=\"t01f9703b8b54b5eb05.jpg?size=562x797\"/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    美丽的女神，拥着自己的优势，虽然是苗条型美女，但在裙子的勾勒下，让她变得十分完美，她女神的风范变得难以抵档，拥有如此极致美感，当然也会让她显得吸引力十足了！\n</p>\n<p>\n    <br/>\n</p>', '1568714159');
INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('522', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">没抢到周杰伦演唱会的票？没关系，新歌来了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">时隔一年零四个月，粉丝的百般催促下，周杰伦终于推出了新歌《说好不哭》，今晚23点已经正式上线了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">别担心，是方文山作的词，以钢琴为主故事线、弦乐编织出抒情场景，再搭配与阿信的对唱，一首典型的周氏情歌。此处应有掌声，粉丝可以哭了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><img alt=\"周杰伦新歌《说好不哭》搞崩QQ，200万粉丝仿佛过年\" src=\"https://img.36krcdn.com/20190917/v2_1568651019368_img_000\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">毕竟上一张专辑《周杰伦的床边故事》是2016年发行，上一首单曲是489天前的《不爱我就拉倒》。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">仿佛过年，《说好不哭》一上线，瞬间杀入微博热搜，立刻就引发了讨论，又一场周氏情歌爱好者的狂欢。上线5分钟，评论上涨近万条，上线25分钟销售数据上涨近40万，QQ音乐手机客户端崩盘。</p><h2 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\">01.打榜风波之后的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\">夕阳红后援团第一次实绩</span></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">粉丝有多期待？</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">方文山在自己的微博中放出了一张自己写的歌词，大量杰迷涌入，误以为那是新歌《说好不哭》中的歌词，纷纷留言催促作曲——“赶紧让那个谁，起来作曲啊。”随后方文山澄清该歌词并非周杰伦新歌歌词，才算停歇。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micr