SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">没有人会质疑周杰伦歌曲的销售数据，但上个月的打榜闹剧，的确也激起了部分杰迷们的好胜心。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">与过往的新歌上线有些许不同，不论是《等你下课》还是调侃了许久的《不爱我就拉倒》更不用说更早以前的《晴天》，几乎没有歌迷会在评论区讨论销量的问题，大家都忙着书写青春。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">但《说好不哭》的QQ音乐评论区，罕见的出现了是否该为周杰伦冲销量的讨论。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inheri