量超110万《床边故事》，购买用户前三名加起来也不过1223张，前五名加起来都未超过3000张。（《等你下课》《不爱我就拉倒》均为免费）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">但，尽管单人（官方后援会）购买的数量有了一定程度的攀升，谁也不敢轻易说周杰伦也得靠数据，毕竟，排在总榜第一的专辑，还有着第一席位买6万张的成绩。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; word-break: break-word; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; white-space: normal;\">或许，周杰伦新歌的狂欢告诉我们的是，对于当下的华语音乐而言，缺的根本不是销量，而是上线后的传唱度，“没考上跟你一样的大学”也好，“胸肌”也罢，说到底都来自音乐本身，而不是没有人听过的销售冠军。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeitiSC-Light, simsun, 宋体, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; -we