ground-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这位美女选择的是一袭墨绿色的吊带连衣裤出行。美女有着一头波浪式长发，白皙干净的皮肤，精致的容妆，高挑挺拔的身材。连衣裤的吊带和深V设计很好的展现出了美女的胸部曲线。微收腰的设计显得美女腰部纤细，腰线很高，很好的拉长了上下半身比。连衣裤的紧身打底裤设计有着很好的塑形效果，能够很好的打造出宽胯，翘臀，大长腿的属性。搭配一双高跟凉鞋，更显的身材高挑挺拔。</p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"670\" height=\"1212.2533333333\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568726707966485.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"670\" height=\"1005\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568726707354752.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">吊带连衣裤的背部也是非常时尚的交叉系带露背设计，能够很好的展示肩部和背部曲线。整体的服装造型和搭配相对简约，给人一种非常时尚新潮的感觉。不过小编想说，连衣裤装的确时尚性感，但美女上厕所是不是麻烦了一点？！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\