INSERT INTO `yxd_news_data` VALUES ('526', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">学院风的女生，给人带来一种青涩的时尚感。外表清纯，搭配上也有一种简单、好看。给人的第一印象就是清爽，没有过多的修饰、做作痕迹。今天，跟随小编来看一下这种学院风格打扮的网红美女，透着一种清新自然味道。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"605\" height=\"839\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568726817399925.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">画面上的小姐姐站在小湖边上，一身清爽的打扮，让她有一种舒适的美感。扎着马尾，能很好的突显出她的气质。一身淡雅妆束的形象，让她的美呈现出一种没有瑕疵的少女形象。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><img class=\"scrollLoading\" width=\"604\" height=\"839\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190917/1568726817361348.jpeg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 12px 0px; outline: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); f